---
/**
 * Process Isolation & Virtual Memory diagram.
 * Shows how two processes have isolated virtual memory spaces
 * that map to different physical addresses.
 */
---

<div class="ipc-diagram process-isolation not-prose">
  <div class="diagram-container">
    <h2 class="diagram-title">프로세스 격리와 가상 메모리</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">같은 주소 0x1000이 물리적으로 전혀 다른 곳을 가리킵니다</p>
    <div class="diagram">
      <div class="process-box process-a">
        <div class="process-header">Process A</div>
        <div class="virtual-mem">
          <div class="label">Virtual Memory</div>
          <div class="addr-range">0x0000 ~ 0xFFFF</div>
        </div>
        <div class="arrow-section">
          <div class="arrow-down"></div><div class="arrow-tip"></div>
          <div class="page-table">Page Table A</div>
          <div class="arrow-down"></div><div class="arrow-tip"></div>
          <div class="physical-mem physical-a">0x7A00 ~ 0x7AFF</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="wall"><div class="wall-line"></div><div class="wall-badge">격리됨</div></div>
      <div class="process-box process-b">
        <div class="process-header">Process B</div>
        <div class="virtual-mem">
          <div class="label">Virtual Memory</div>
          <div class="addr-range">0x0000 ~ 0xFFFF</div>
        </div>
        <div class="arrow-section">
          <div class="arrow-down"></div><div class="arrow-tip"></div>
          <div class="page-table">Page Table B</div>
          <div class="arrow-down"></div><div class="arrow-tip"></div>
          <div class="physical-mem physical-b">0x3B00 ~ 0x3BFF</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="callout">
      <strong>왜 IPC가 필요한가:</strong> 이 격리 덕분에 프로세스 하나가 죽어도 다른 프로세스에 영향을 주지 않습니다. 하지만 바로 이 격리 때문에 프로세스끼리 데이터를 주고받으려면 OS의 도움이 필요합니다.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .process-isolation {
    --bg: #ffffff;
    --surface: #f5f7fa;
    --card: #ffffff;
    --border: #e4e4e4;
    --border-dashed: #c8cdd5;
    --text: #1e2231;
    --text-muted: #5a6478;
    --code-bg: #f0f2f5;
    --accent: #0078ff;
    --accent-bg: #e8f1ff;
    --accent-border: #b3d4ff;
    --process-a: #0078ff;
    --process-a-bg: #e8f1ff;
    --process-a-header: #edf4ff;
    --process-b: #8957e5;
    --process-b-bg: #f3edff;
    --process-b-header: #f5f0ff;
    --wall-color: #e5534b;
    --wall-bg: #fff1f0;
    --wall-border: #e5534b;
  }

  :global(.dark) .process-isolation {
    --bg: #171c2a;
    --surface: #1e2331;
    --card: #171c2a;
    --border: #2a3042;
    --border-dashed: #3a4258;
    --text: #ffffff;
    --text-muted: #8892a4;
    --code-bg: #1e2331;
    --accent: #0078ff;
    --accent-bg: #0c2d5e;
    --accent-border: #0a4a99;
    --process-a: #0078ff;
    --process-a-bg: #0c2d5e;
    --process-a-header: #0c2d5e;
    --process-b: #bc8cff;
    --process-b-bg: #231a33;
    --process-b-header: #2a1f3f;
    --wall-color: #f85149;
    --wall-bg: #3d1114;
    --wall-border: #6e2b2b;
  }

  .diagram-container {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 48px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .diagram-title {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .diagram {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 60px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .process-box {
    width: 240px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .process-box:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .process-header {
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 14px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .process-a .process-header {
    background: var(--process-a-header);
    color: var(--process-a);
  }

  .process-b .process-header {
    background: var(--process-b-header);
    color: var(--process-b);
  }

  .virtual-mem {
    padding: 16px;
    background: var(--card);
  }

  .virtual-mem .label {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .addr-range {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'SF Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    background: var(--code-bg);
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .arrow-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 8px 16px 16px;
  }

  .arrow-down {
    width: 2px;
    height: 24px;
    background: var(--border-dashed);
  }

  .arrow-tip {
    width: 0;
    height: 0;
    border-left: 6px solid transparent;
    border-right: 6px solid transparent;
    border-top: 8px solid var(--border-dashed);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .page-table {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border: 1px dashed var(--border-dashed);
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .physical-mem {
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'SF Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .physical-a {
    background: var(--process-a-bg);
    color: var(--process-a);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-border);
  }

  .physical-b {
    background: var(--process-b-bg);
    color: var(--process-b);
    border: 1px solid var(--process-b);
  }

  .wall {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .wall-line {
    width: 2px;
    height: 100%;
    position: absolute;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      var(--wall-color) 0px,
      var(--wall-color) 6px,
      transparent 6px,
      transparent 12px
    );
  }

  .wall-badge {
    background: var(--wall-bg);
    color: var(--wall-color);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--wall-border);
    z-index: 1;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .callout {
    margin-top: 24px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: var(--accent-bg);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .callout strong {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .diagram-container {
      padding: 24px 16px;
    }

    .diagram {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .wall {
      position: static;
      transform: none;
      flex-direction: row;
    }

    .wall-line {
      width: 100%;
      height: 2px;
      position: static;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        to right,
        var(--wall-color) 0px,
        var(--wall-color) 6px,
        transparent 6px,
        transparent 12px
      );
    }
  }
</style>
